              How to apply
            </h2>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
              Get a digital passport photo
            </h3>
            <p class="govuk-body">
              We’ll show you how to get a digital photo.
            </p>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
              Apply and pay online
            </h3>
            <p class="govuk-body">
              A standard passport costs £75.50.
            </p>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
              Ask someone to confirm your identity
            </h3>
            <p class="govuk-body">
              They can <a href='#' class='govuk-link'>confirm your identity online</a> without a printed photo.
            </p>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
              Send us your documents
            </h3>
            <p class="govuk-body">
              They need to be originals. We’ll tell you what you need to send.
            </p>
            <h3 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
              Go for an interview
            </h3>
            <p class="govuk-body">
              If you need an <a href='#' class='govuk-link'>interview</a>, we’ll write to you with the details.
            </p>
            <button class="govuk-button govuk-!-margin-top-3" data-module="govuk-button">
              Continue
